<article articleID="LBr9_00266_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence>　一時間、二時間後に、追手が追い<sampling type="start" />ついてくるということはないだろう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「追手の方が、多少は速いだろう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　御門が言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　しかし、追手が獣化兵ならば話は別だ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　獣化兵が、本隊から離れて、単独で追ってくるのなら、三十分後に追いつかれる可能性もある。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　獣化兵はふたり。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　そのふたりが、一緒に、本隊から分かれて追ってくることはないだろう。</sentence>
<sentence>そうすると、後続の本隊に、臭いをたどることのできる者がいなくなり、後を追えなくなるからだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もし、先行してくるのなら、獣化兵がひとり。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「法山は、おそらく、獣化兵のひとりを、先に行かせているだろう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能が言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「だろうな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　通訳をした男―ワカンが言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「この近くに、たてこもって、法山たちと闘うのにいい場所はあるか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能が訊いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ない」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ワカンが首を左右に振った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「基本的には、どこも、この場所と同じだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あるとするなら、神殿だけだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「しかし、神殿にこのまま行ってしまっていいのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「まずいな、それは」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ワカンが言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「夜が明けて、夕方まで逃げきることができれば、おそらくスコールが降る。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">そうすれば、向こうも臭いをたどることはできない」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ならば、決まったな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能が、あっさりとした口調で言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どう決まったんだ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ワカンが言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「何人かが残って、追手をしばらく足止めする。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">明日の夕方、スコールがくるまでだ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「その後で、どこかで合流するか、神殿までたどり着く」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「先行して逃げる方は、とりあえず、神殿とは別の方向に進む。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">スコールが降った時点で、神殿へ方向を変えればいい―」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「わかった。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">しかし―」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「しかし、何だ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「誰が、追手を足止めする役をやるんだ。</sentence>
<sentence>リスクが大きすぎるぞ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">何人残るかわからんが、メンバーの中から必ず死人が出るだろう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おれがやる」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あんたが？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「最初にやってくる獣化兵だけは、間違いなく倒しておく。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">後は―」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「後は？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「薬師丸法山だけだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　きっぱりと、久能は言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="はら">肚</ruby>をすえた声であった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「死ぬ覚悟を決めているのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「さあな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「日本人の好きなバンザイ・アタックか。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">おれたちのためにそこまでする義理があんたにあるのか」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「義理はないよ。</sentence>
<sentence>あんたたちのためじゃない。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">おれのために、おれのためだけにおれはやるんだよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能は言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あんたは、おれに、ここからどの方向に何キロ行けば神殿があるかを教えてくれればいい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それで、おれにはわかる」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「それで、神殿まで来ることができるのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「生きていればな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「北東へ、十七キロ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ワカンは言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「わかった」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能はうなずいた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「行け」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　久能は言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おまえ、本当に独りでやるのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ああ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「本気か」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おれに考えがある」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どんな考えだ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「説明している時間はない」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おれも残る」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ワカンが言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いいのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「日本人にだけ、そんなことをさせられないね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　ワカンが言った時、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ぼくも残るよ…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　低い声で、チムが言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おまえが？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「薬師丸法山は、ぼくが<sampling type="end" />殺すよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">あんたには殺させない」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
